title: Grand Theft Auto IV (GTA 4) - Episodes From Liberty City - OST [
description:
Here's the complete and uncompressed soundtrack of Grand Theft Auto IV : Episodes From Liberty City!

As the files where in a mess in the game directories, I joined the two episodes into one big soundtrack. There are only the alternate versions of the existing stations of GTA IV, as well as the new ones.

Some stations are a mix, some consist of a mix and stand-alone tracks, others are only split up tracks. I included all I had, and tagged everything so it would be consistent.
Also included, all the news, commercials, host interventions (sometimes separated into 2 sets, coming from TBGT or TLAD), weather reports.
Also included, the loading and menu tracks for the whole and both of the episodes.
Also included, the mix we can hear at Hercules' gay club.

Enjoy! And seed!
